?source=172ae18b"><meta itemprop="url" content="https://www.zhihu.com/people/zhang-hu-45-98"><meta itemprop="zhihu:followerCount"><span class="UserLink AuthorInfo-avatarWrapper"><div class="Popover"><div id="Popover7-toggle" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false" aria-owns="Popover7-content"><a class="UserLink-link" data-za-detail-view-element_name="User" target="_blank" href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/zhang-hu-45-98"><img class="Avatar Avatar--round AuthorInfo-avatar" width="38" height="38" src="./RampMap_files/2908f45efc70d715f71046cb3914d2b2_xs.jpg" srcset="https://pic4.zhimg.com/2908f45efc70d715f71046cb3914d2b2_l.jpg?source=172ae18b 2x" alt="张鹄"></a></div></div></span><div class="AuthorInfo-content"><div class="AuthorInfo-head"><span class="UserLink AuthorInfo-name"><div class="Popover"><div id="Popover8-toggle" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false" aria-owns="Popover8-content"><a class="UserLink-link" data-za-detail-view-element_name="User" target="_blank" href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/zhang-hu-45-98">张鹄</a></div></div></span></div><div class="AuthorInfo-detail"><div class="AuthorInfo-badge"><div class="ztext AuthorInfo-badgeText">我就看看不说话</div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="LabelContainer-wrapper"></div><div><span class="Voters"><button type="button" class="Button Button--plain">43 人<!-- -->赞同了该文章</button></span></div></header><div class="Post-RichTextContainer"><div class="RichText ztext Post-RichText"><p>上节说到了皮肤的光影比普通标准光影，有两个显著的区别</p><ol><li>明暗交接处，有明显的颜色过度，白色-&gt;红色-&gt;黑色</li><li>皮肤的凹凸感很弱很柔和</li></ol><p>那么由此就引出了本节要介绍的一个皮肤渲染方法，预积分的皮肤RampMap方法。</p><p>那么我们还是从基础说起，这个RampMap是个啥玩意呢？这个东西其实听古老的了，在卡通渲染方面很常用，早在07年阀门厂关于军团要塞2的那篇文章里就有说过。</p><p>还是上图，左边的图来自军团要塞2的论文，右边的图来自我的UE截图</p><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7553bbd27bc1626cf433963f509230b2_b.jpg" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="777" data-rawheight="311" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="777" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7553bbd27bc1626cf433963f509230b2_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="./RampMap_files/v2-7553bbd27bc1626cf433963f509230b2_720w.jpg" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="777" data-rawheight="311" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="777" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7553bbd27bc1626cf433963f509230b2_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7553bbd27bc1626cf433963f509230b2_b.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok"><figcaption>卡通渲染漫反射和标准漫反射对比</figcaption></figure><p>右边这个球是标准的漫反射的样子，光从右上方照射，把球的一半点亮。但是我们能看到，这个明暗的对比度是很强的，这个在卡通渲染那边是很不想见到的，卡通渲染都是对比度很弱的，暗部阴影区也希望有一定的亮度，甚至说还希望通过冷暖色调来表现阴影，而不是这种单纯的明暗。</p><p>那么这样的话，就需要很强的自由度，能让美术同学自由的选择明暗区域对应的颜色，那么很自然的就想到了查找表的方法，我首先提取每个像素的亮度，然后根据这个亮度值去查表，然后把查表的结果写入像素，这样不就行了么，很自由。那么这里的查找表是什么的，就是一张图，就是我们说的RampMap，军团要塞2中使用的查找表如下。</p><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-3c6f5adb9b0649c3d401a7cb3062e31d_b.png" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="888" data-rawheight="62" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="888" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-3c6f5adb9b0649c3d401a7cb3062e31d_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="./RampMap_files/v2-3c6f5adb9b0649c3d401a7cb3062e31d_720w.png" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="888" data-rawheight="62" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="888" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-3c6f5adb9b0649c3d401a7cb3062e31d_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-3c6f5adb9b0649c3d401a7cb3062e31d_b.png" data-lazy-status="ok"><figcaption>军团要塞2的RampMap</figcaption></figure><p>这张图是一个一维图，也就是它纵向只有一个像素宽，上图为了方便展示拉伸了。他的横坐标代表标准漫反射亮度，从左到右代表亮度为0~1，下面给出了简单的代码。注意亮度需要乘0.5再加0.5，因为亮度的范围是-1~1的，而采图需要0~1范围的数。</p><p>asd</p><p class="ztext-empty-paragraph"><br></p><p>//N: 物体表明法线 垂直于物体表明 指向外<br>//L: 光线方向 从物体当前点 指向光源方向<br>//RampMap RampMapSampler RampMap贴图及采样器<br>float brightness = dot(N, L);<br>float2 sampleUV = float2(brightness*0.5 + 0.5, 0.5);<br>return RampMap.Sample(RampMapSampler, sampleUV);</p><p>注意看的话可以看到，RampMap在明暗交接部分有些发红，在实际漫反射效果图里，也可以看到人物的明暗交接区有些泛红。这是美术同学特意制作的，用来模仿手绘的水彩画边缘的效果。既然这种图，可以用来修改物体的明暗区域，以及交接线的颜色，而且它的自由度由如此之大，那么我们为什么不用它来模拟皮肤呢，毕竟皮肤边缘也有这种颜色过度啊。</p><p>那么下面一个问题就是，如何获取真实的皮肤的这种颜色过渡呢？让美术同学手绘么？好像也行，但是恐怕真实感就要打折扣了。好在这个问题早就有人解决了，在NV的 GPU Gem3的14章，提及了皮肤的光线扩散理论，并给出了用“累加六个带权重的高斯项”的方法，拟合真实的扩散曲线，系数请看下图。</p><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-60a5613e2624c9a259ea0e9403c40778_b.jpg" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="1026" data-rawheight="442" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1026" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-60a5613e2624c9a259ea0e9403c40778_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="./RampMap_files/v2-60a5613e2624c9a259ea0e9403c40778_720w.jpg" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="1026" data-rawheight="442" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1026" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-60a5613e2624c9a259ea0e9403c40778_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-60a5613e2624c9a259ea0e9403c40778_b.jpg" data-lazy-status="ok"><figcaption>六高斯的方差及权重</figcaption></figure><p>高斯函数有两个参数，一个是均值μ，一个是方差σ2，μ就是对称轴，σ2就是偏离程度，偏离越小曲线就越集中越高。显然此处对称轴μ=0，σ2方差表中第一列给出了，那就很简单了，我们可以开始写代码计算了，下面给出代码。（这些数是怎么算出来的，我比较菜是搞不明白的，如果有谁对这个感兴趣，可以查查别的资料。）</p><div class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-cpp"><span class="c1">//高斯函数 v就是方差 r就是自变量x，在上图中表示偏移的距离
</span><span class="c1"></span><span class="kt">float</span> <span class="nf">Gaussian</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">float</span> <span class="n">v</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="kt">float</span> <span class="n">r</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="p">{</span>
    <span class="k">return</span> <span class="mf">1.0</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="n">sqrt</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mf">2.0f</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">PI</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">v</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">*</span><span class="n">exp</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">r</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">r</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mf">2.0f</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">v</span><span class="p">));</span>
<span class="p">}</span>

<span class="n">float3</span> <span class="nf">Scatter</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">float</span> <span class="n">r</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="p">{</span>
    <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">Gaussian</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mf">0.0064f</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="mf">1.414f</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">r</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">float3</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mf">0.233f</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">0.455f</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">0.649f</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">+</span>
	<span class="n">Gaussian</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mf">0.0484f</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="mf">1.414f</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">r</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">float3</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mf">0.100f</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">0.336f</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">0.344f</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">+</span>
	<span class="n">Gaussian</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mf">0.1870f</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="mf">1.414f</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">r</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">float3</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mf">0.118f</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">0.198f</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">0.000f</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">+</span>
	<span class="n">Gaussian</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mf">0.5670f</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="mf">1.414f</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">r</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">float3</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mf">0.113f</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">0.007f</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">0.007f</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">+</span>
	<span class="n">Gaussian</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mf">1.9900f</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="mf">1.414f</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">r</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">float3</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mf">0.358f</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">0.004f</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">0.000f</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">+</span>
	<span class="n">Gaussian</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mf">7.4100f</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="mf">1.414f</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">r</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">float3</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mf">0.078f</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">0.000f</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">0.000f</span><span class="p">);</span>
<span class="p">}</span>
</code></pre></div><p>好，现在有了计算“一束光照在皮肤上时，周围的点受影响情况”的方法，那么预积分就来了。皮肤实际受光时，必然是一片皮肤都受到了光线的直接照射，不可能只有一个点受直接照射。那么，皮肤上的某一个点，就必然受它周围所有点的光照影响，因为光线从它周围的点入射皮肤，并在皮肤内传播，然后到达了这个点。</p><p>那么，这个点实际受光 = 这个点直接受光 + 周围所有点对他的间接影响。而周围所有点有多少个呢？无穷多个。需要累加无穷多项，那就要计算积分了。</p><p>虽然从逻辑上来说，我们应该对物体表面上的所有点进行积分，但是要注意，我们的目标只是想要获取一个皮肤的颜色偏向，并不是要严格求解一个物理公式，人眼对颜色的容忍度是很高的，只要差不多就可以了。所以这里对这个问题进行了两个简化。</p><ol><li>假设物体是一个球体。</li><li>不在整个球面上积分，改为在球的一个环上积分。</li></ol><p>在球的表明积分就完事了，多简单啊，整一个不规则体积分都算不出来。而事实证明，球面积分和环积分算出来的颜色差别不大，而环积分更简单，球面积分还需要二重积分多麻烦。</p><p>这里还有一个问题，球体半径还没确定啊。实际生活中是这样，弯曲程度大的表面，往往比较薄，光更容易穿透，次表明散射现象更明显，对应到球上就是半径比较小的球体。同理，半径比较大的球体，不怎么弯曲的表明，次表明散射现象就比较弱。也就是说，真对不同的半径应该有不同样子的颜色过度，那么我们这个一维的查找表，很自然的就扩展到了二维。横坐标还是表示亮度，纵坐标表示球体半径或曲率（半径的倒数）。</p><p>那么我们来看看具体的计算过程，还是上图</p><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e52ecda1cfab3bbdffb6f6b590972b85_b.jpg" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="842" data-rawheight="377" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="842" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e52ecda1cfab3bbdffb6f6b590972b85_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;842&#39; height=&#39;377&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="842" data-rawheight="377" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="842" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e52ecda1cfab3bbdffb6f6b590972b85_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e52ecda1cfab3bbdffb6f6b590972b85_b.jpg"><figcaption>积分过程讲解图</figcaption></figure><p>这个图和上面那个图都来自SIGGRAPH2011的公开课程，有兴趣的可以点链接</p><a target="_blank" href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//advances.realtimerendering.com/s2011/" data-draft-node="block" data-draft-type="link-card" data-image="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-07dea5b53ec3e3a4ea3d07e1bef723f4_180x120.jpg" data-image-width="1258" data-image-height="161" class="LinkCard LinkCard--hasImage"><span class="LinkCard-backdrop" style="background-image:url(https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-07dea5b53ec3e3a4ea3d07e1bef723f4_180x120.jpg)"></span><span class="LinkCard-content"><span class="LinkCard-text"><span class="LinkCard-title" data-text="true">Advances in Real-Time Rendering in 3D Graphics and Games</span><span class="LinkCard-meta"><span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--InsertLink" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="17" height="17"><path d="M13.414 4.222a4.5 4.5 0 1 1 6.364 6.364l-3.005 3.005a.5.5 0 0 1-.707 0l-.707-.707a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.707l3.005-3.005a2.5 2.5 0 1 0-3.536-3.536l-3.005 3.005a.5.5 0 0 1-.707 0l-.707-.707a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.707l3.005-3.005zm-6.187 6.187a.5.5 0 0 1 .638-.058l.07.058.706.707a.5.5 0 0 1 .058.638l-.058.07-3.005 3.004a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 3.405 3.658l.13-.122 3.006-3.005a.5.5 0 0 1 .638-.058l.069.058.707.707a.5.5 0 0 1 .058.638l-.058.069-3.005 3.005a4.5 4.5 0 0 1-6.524-6.196l.16-.168 3.005-3.005zm8.132-3.182a.25.25 0 0 1 .353 0l1.061 1.06a.25.25 0 0 1 0 .354l-8.132 8.132a.25.25 0 0 1-.353 0l-1.061-1.06a.25.25 0 0 1 0-.354l8.132-8.132z"></path></svg></span>advances.realtimerendering.com</span></span><span class="LinkCard-imageCell"><img class="LinkCard-image LinkCard-image--horizontal" alt="图标" src="./RampMap_files/v2-07dea5b53ec3e3a4ea3d07e1bef723f4_180x120.jpg"></span></span></a><p>图左部分就是在说高斯拟合函数，这个函数需要一个距离作为输入，因为要求和很多周围的点，然后每个周围的点到当前点的距离，就是这个输入。这是一个数值积分过程，利用实际计算大量的点求和，再取平均的方式求积分，量越大越准确，具体细节可以搜索蒙特卡洛积分。</p><p>图的右部分就是在说沿着圆环进行积分，N那个剪头代表当前点，其上每一个小黑点，都代表它周围的点，都需要计算一次左图的函数，因为距离是弧长，比较不好计算，而且可以看到偏离N远了之后，这个函数就很弱了，约等于0，这个时候算错了无所谓了，反正都很弱。干脆用弦长代替弧长，还好算。</p><p>这个图有个小问题，θ实际代表的是N和L的夹角，而N和N+θ的夹角应该是公式里的x。而且图中公式没有给出半径，因为这是举例，半径设为1，我们要针对不同半径都进行一遍计算。另外就是图中小黑点过多，因为N方向的背面半球全黑，根本不需要计算。</p><p>OK，下面可以给出实际的RampMap生成代码了</p><div class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-cpp"><span class="c1">//////////Generate RampMap////////////
</span><span class="c1">//UV就是烘焙图片的UV
</span><span class="c1"></span><span class="kt">float</span> <span class="n">NoL</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">UV</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">x</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="mi">2</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="c1">//还是那个问题 NoL应该是 -1到1 的范围
</span><span class="c1"></span><span class="kt">float</span> <span class="n">Radius</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mf">1.0</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="n">max</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">UV</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">y</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">0.001</span><span class="p">);</span>

<span class="kt">float</span> <span class="n">theta</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">acos</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">NoL</span><span class="p">);</span>
<span class="n">float3</span> <span class="n">totalWeights</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">float3</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">);</span>
<span class="n">float3</span> <span class="n">totalDiffuse</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">float3</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">);</span>

<span class="kt">float</span> <span class="n">StepDist</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">PI</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="n">SampleSteps</span><span class="p">;</span>

<span class="kt">float</span> <span class="n">x</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="n">PI</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="mf">0.5f</span><span class="p">;</span>
<span class="k">while</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">x</span> <span class="o">&lt;=</span> <span class="n">PI</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="mf">0.5f</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="p">{</span>
    <span class="kt">float</span> <span class="n">Diffuse</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">max</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">cos</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">theta</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">x</span><span class="p">),</span> <span class="mf">0.0f</span><span class="p">);</span>
    <span class="kt">float</span> <span class="n">SampleDist</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">abs</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mf">2.0f</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">Radius</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="n">sin</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="mf">0.5f</span><span class="p">));</span>
    
    <span class="n">float3</span> <span class="n">curWeight</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">Scatter</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">SampleDist</span><span class="p">);</span>
    <span class="n">totalWeights</span> <span class="o">+=</span> <span class="n">curWeight</span><span class="p">;</span>
    <span class="n">totalDiffuse</span> <span class="o">+=</span> <span class="n">Diffuse</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">curWeight</span><span class="p">;</span>
    <span class="n">x</span> <span class="o">+=</span> <span class="n">StepDist</span><span class="p">;</span>
<span class="p">}</span>
<span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">totalDiffuse</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="n">totalWeights</span><span class="p">;</span>
</code></pre></div><p>Ok执行！你会得到如下的一张图片，其实光看这张图片就能感受到光照透皮肤的感觉了。这张图来自UE执行上述代码的结果</p><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f917d2f1d4681dc031f656714f3d84b5_b.jpg" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="418" data-rawheight="418" class="content_image" width="418"/></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;418&#39; height=&#39;418&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="418" data-rawheight="418" class="content_image lazy" width="418" data-actualsrc="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f917d2f1d4681dc031f656714f3d84b5_b.jpg"><figcaption>SkinRampMap</figcaption></figure><p>好下面放到模型上去看看，看起来效果还不错，下图是UE截图</p><figure data-size="normal"><noscript><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-889bf8c8d78982eac7d4930d98abb0a6_b.jpg" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="734" data-rawheight="329" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="734" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-889bf8c8d78982eac7d4930d98abb0a6_r.jpg"/></noscript><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;734&#39; height=&#39;329&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="734" data-rawheight="329" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="734" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-889bf8c8d78982eac7d4930d98abb0a6_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-889bf8c8d78982eac7d4930d98abb0a6_b.jpg"><figcaption>效果图 从左到右 半径分别是 1 2 4 8</figcaption></figure><p>好本节就到这里，到目前为止，我们生成了一张RampMap，并且读取这张图的UV的x坐标已经有了(NdotL)，还缺少y坐标，也就是半径信息</p><p>下一节说一说如何获取模型表面的半径参数，也就是模型曲率计算</p></div></div><div class="ContentItem-time">发布于 2020-05-16</div><div class="Post-topicsAndReviewer"><div class="TopicList Post-Topics"><div class="Tag Topic" data-za-detail-view-path-module="TopicItem" data-za-extra-module="{&quot;card&quot;:{&quot;content&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;Topic&quot;,&quot;token&quot;:&quot;19613730&quot;}}}"><span class="Tag-content"><a class="TopicLink" h